{
  "id": "S2CHNG12",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "132 COLUMN SUPPORT",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "CHANGES"
  },
  "type": "changelog",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You can now work with any extended display modes that your system"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "supports, including the 132 column modes supplied by many of the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Super VGA cards."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To use extended video modes, setup your DOS or OS/2 session prior"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "to getting into SPF/PC.   Upon entering SPF/PC (as long as the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SCREEN LINES field of Panel 0.1 is set to 0), SPF/PC will detect"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the alternate video mode and adjust automatically."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In OS/2, alternate video modes must be first supported by your OS/2"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "video driver and are usually selected using the OS/2 Mode command."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In DOS, alternate video modes are selected using software shipped"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "with your video adapter. See your adapter documention for details."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For further details see:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC User Guide and Reference,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Terminal Characteristics Option 0.1 ....... Page 9-3"
      }
    ]
  },
  "proc_section": {
    "assignments": {
      "ZSEL": "UP"
    }
  },
  "metadata": {
    "source_file": "S2CHNG12.PAN",
    "category": "changelog"
  }
}